    sub_lat = df.loc[i, ""]
    sub_long = df.loc[i, ""]
    
    title = "{}".format(df.loc[i, ''])

m
m.save('folium1.html')

## data load
df = pd.read_table('data/seoul_starbucks.txt', sep='|')
df

color_dic={ '': 'gray','': 'lightgray','': 'lightcoral','': 'darkred','': 'red',
            '': 'coral','': 'chocolate','': 'peachpuff','': 'darkorange','': 'gold',
            '': 'olive','': 'chartreuse','': 'darkseagreen','': 'green','': 'teal',
            '': 'deepskyblue','': 'lightslategray','': 'navy','': 'mediumpurple','': 'violet',
            '': 'orchid','': 'crimson','': 'pink','': 'cyan','': 'purple'}

m= folium.Map([df[""].mean(), df[""].mean()], zoom_start=12, tiles='CartoDB positron')

for i in df.index:
    sub_lat = df.loc[i, ""]
    sub_long = df.loc[i, ""]
    gu=df.loc[i,'']
    title = "{}".format(df.loc[i, ''])
    
    _=folium.CircleMarker([sub_lat, sub_long], color=color_dic[gu], tooltip=title, radius=6).add_to(m)
m
m.save('folium2.html')

## data load
df = pd.read_csv('data/seoul_starbucks.txt', sep='|')

fig=plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4), dpi=150)
ax1, ax2 =fig.subplots(1,2)

## ax1
_=ax1.scatter(df[''], df[''], edgecolor='k')

## ax2
color_dic={ '': 'gray','': 'lightgray','': 'lightcoral','': 'darkred','': 'red',
            '': 'coral','': 'chocolate','': 'peachpuff','': 'darkorange','': 'gold',
            '': 'olive','': 'chartreuse','': 'darkseagreen','': 'green','': 'teal',
            '': 'deepskyblue','': 'lightslategray','': 'navy','': 'mediumpurple','': 'violet',
            '': 'orchid','': 'crimson','': 'pink','': 'cyan','': 'purple'}

for gu in df[''].unique():
    df1=df.loc[df['']==gu]
    _=ax2.scatter(df1[''], df1[''], edgecolor='k', color=color_dic[gu], label=gu)

ax2.legend(loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1), ncol=3)
_=ax2.set_xticks(np.arange(126.8, 127.2,0.1))
_=ax2.grid()
